### Why choose TrimFlex?

- **Maximum detail** — Reproduces complex logos with millimetric precision
- **Light reflection** — Finishes that capture attention from every angle
- **Durability** — Resistant to industrial washing and prolonged exposure
- **Versatility** — Available as heat transfer, sticker, embroidered badge, velcro or pin

### Application process

TrimFlex emblems are applied using heat and pressure, permanently bonding to the garment and guaranteeing a lasting hold that withstands more than 60 continuous wash cycles. We also offer self-adhesive TrimFlex for use on rigid surfaces such as thermoses, mugs, bottles, and even automobiles.
